
Set of files to map for HL1 and mods.
The contents of the folder are intended to be located in the "valve" directory.

zhlt.wad..................common textures (trigger, clip, hint etc.)
common_vhlt.shader........shader, making common textures to look transparent
common_hlbasics.shader....shader, making extra common textures to look transparent


**build menu is configured with VHLT compiler in mind;
  (https://twhl.info/wiki/page/Tools_and_Resources#Compile_Tools)
  just drop binaries to radiant folder, in a "ZHLT" subfolder